Package ohos.ai.asr.util

Class AsrResultKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.asr.util.AsrResultKey

  • public class AsrResultKey
extends Object
    Stores the keywords in ASR callback results.

    During ASR method calls, some callbacks in AsrListener return result data containing keywords.

    3
